org.eclipse.emf.compare.ide.ui.internal.contentmergeviewer

Class MirrorUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.compare.ide.ui.internal.contentmergeviewer.MirrorUtil

  • public class MirrorUtil
extends Object
    A utility class to handle the common functionality of mirroring the content merge viewer sides, i.e., swapping the left and right viewer. The mirroring functionality was introduced in Eclipse Compare v3.7 and therefore needs to be handled reflectively to avoid backwards compatibility issues.
